flower birth day

pander::pander(flow,
               caption = "day of the flower birth")
function (. = NULL, .value = NULL, ...) 
{
    flow_class <- c("Flow", "proto", "environment")
    if (!is_flow(.)) {
        root <- structure(proto(.GlobalEnv, envir = child_env2(.GlobalEnv), 
            .value = NULL, .call = NULL, .name = "root"), class = flow_class)
        if (!missing(.value)) 
            . <- .value
        structure(do_call(proto, c(list(root, envir = child_env2(root), 
            .value = .), quos_underscore(...))), class = flow_class)
    }
    else {
        args_list <- list(., envir = child_env2(.))
        if (!missing(.value)) 
            args_list$.value <- .value
        structure(do_call(proto, c(args_list, quos_underscore(...))), 
            class = flow_class)
    }
}
